      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p class="text-text-muted"><strong>Last updated:</strong> November 30, 2024</p>

      <p>How To Use Internet ("us", "we", or "our") operates the How To Use Internet website (the "Service"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service.</p>

      <h2>Summary</h2>

      <p class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-lg"><strong>We do not collect any personal data.</strong> Our website is a static educational resource that does not use cookies, analytics, tracking scripts, or any form of data collection. Your privacy is fully respected.</p>

